The paper deals with machine learning and data mining, specifically in the context of multi-target regression in data streams. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) or Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a new online learning strategy, which could also place it in the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The use of decision trees and inter-target dependencies in the proposed strategy could also suggest a connection to Computer Vision (cs.CV) or Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
